19
00:02:18,783 --> 00:02:20,869
When I end up lying there…

20
00:02:23,163 --> 00:02:24,247
who do you think…

21
00:02:26,041 --> 00:02:27,625
will be standing here?

22
00:02:32,088 --> 00:02:33,798
Probably me.

23
00:02:37,343 --> 00:02:38,511
Let's…

24
00:02:41,556 --> 00:02:43,058
get married.

25
00:02:54,069 --> 00:02:57,030
It seems like an artificial joint.
What do you want to do with it?

26
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,869
How does this work?

27
00:03:03,453 --> 00:03:05,872
Well, if you want us to discard it,
we can.

28
00:03:09,417 --> 00:03:11,336
Pack it up, please.

29
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:45,036
LATE KWAK HYE-SUK

30
00:04:03,138 --> 00:04:05,098
Get some sleep, Dad.

31
